high_descs: Make a left and then a right to walk through the other room until you reach the glass coffee table.
Pick up the keys sitting on the glass coffee table.
Turn around to walk around the chairs to reach the tall lamp next to the TV set.
anns.task_desc: Pick up some keys to look at them under a tall lit lamp.

high_descs: Turn left, take a right at the wooden table, head right at the glass table, take a left at the chair and turn left to face the glass table.
Pick up the set of keys next to the gold bottle on the table.
Turn left, take a left at the black desk and walk to the tall lamp on the left.
anns.task_desc: Examine a set of keys by the light of a tall lamp.

high_descs: Turn left walk forward then turn right head to the center table
Pick up the keys on the center table
Turn left then walk towards the lamp
anns.task_desc: Examine the keys by the light
